{"tid":2194010,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"快必以言入罪..","createTime":"2020-09-08T09:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T09:35:23.000Z","uid":18569,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e100dcc9809d064d57606a8638f4eed21379206b","tid":2194010,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"【以言入罪】<br />\n<br />\n快必案中，控方指控以下口號會鼓動同引發對政府及警隊憎恨，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n2. 五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n3. 黑警死全家<br />\n4. 解散警隊<br />\n5. 721唔見人、831打死人、10月1槍殺人<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<br />\n#新聞"},{"pid":"1bce4f17dcd1f80419be08443ba523ee1649c1b6","tid":2194010,"uid":159271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"要無事！"},{"pid":"b338ad11b73574e1eb26aa046ccc015d0e4caa1e","tid":2194010,"uid":6942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"講下都唔得 冇自由了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f743509dddd4f5787863e64c99a15f224d9ccead","tid":2194010,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:09:35.000Z","msg":"On9，就黎舉白紙都唔得"},{"pid":"212f497f726666167397700d96e0ba9fcbb485bb","tid":2194010,"uid":313334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"source link都費事copy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"492b57dfc8a270263f70bf6c06d9987c7e2fb8e5","tid":2194010,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人民力量譚得志（快必）因《刑事罪行條例》中的「煽動文字」被捕，林鄭月娥稱該罪行仍然有效，形容「Nothing to do with freedom of speech」，有人涉嫌觸犯法律，執法機關便要處理，再次重申言論自由不是毫無限制。她指「批評行政長官」不會違法，稱對行政長官及官員的批評「恆如沙數」，「請大家可以放心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077199&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=06da4f16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077199&h=90f0e9f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077199</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果然係軍政府<br />\n批評777同官員ok<br />\n批評黑警就唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過應該屌完777同班狗官<br />\n佢又會反口話言論自由唔係無限制<br />\n又屈人散播仇恨言論 挑起公眾對政府既仇恨"},{"pid":"f49a93d8a08d76c1724049d7b46c50b435dcaf09","tid":2194010,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"死警甴 柒婆話有言論自由 話只係國安?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccbeda081bd024a6d640a6a0016fc68983d916ee","tid":2194010,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"律政師申請加強制裁"},{"pid":"8df14ee722d56bd32a85df65ccadae77e60edef3","tid":2194010,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"国安法都告緊幾個啦，以言入罪一早已經有"},{"pid":"a89b6b028c30a7b95823de1c0f82a2f3e3e8cf70","tid":2194010,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adfaa4f2968ab2b36bc97e4197020738e83135a","tid":2194010,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G24yhTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG24yhTg.jpg&h=b30f2ddc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15d016198692099e83b7d4edda16788e1802cdd1","tid":2194010,"uid":973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"Dllm現代版文字獄<br />\n以言入罪，痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n何妖石鏡泉拉左未？<br />\n講到明要殺人"},{"pid":"0d714d73383cc7bebbc70a945650cd85251b68ee","tid":2194010,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n黑警死全家<br />\n解散警隊<br />\n721唔見人、831